ygData.msgSnippet: when in north freeport, dont talk to any of the guards, they all have Sir for a title, they are all Paladins. Do not enter the Paladin guild nor the cleric
ygData.messageBody:
when in north freeport, dont talk to any of the guards, they all have Sir
for a title, they are all Paladins. Do not enter the Paladin guild nor the
cleric guild either, so I was told. you can walk by the guards, just dont
talk to these wandering guards.

in west freeport, do not go upstair inside the inn, there is a dwarf in
the, and a high elf, that will kill you.

in east freeport, the building on the docks, not the one you go through to
get to the boat, but the one you see after you go through the last building
to get to the boat, the one right in front of you as you exist this last
building (hope you know what I am talking about), do not go in there from
the upper floor, there is an ogre in there that will kill you
